# Canonical memory schema (file-only)

## memory.jsonl format (one JSON object per line)
{
  "key": "booking.confirm",
  "ns": "booking",
  "source_lang": "sv",
  "source": "Bekr√§fta bokning",
  "targets": { "en": "Confirm booking", "de": null, ... },
  "status": { "en": "ok", "de": "missing", ... },
  "placeholder_signature": "{ } / %s / ICU ...",
  "meta": { "description": "CTA button", "screen": "Checkout" },
  "fingerprint": "sha256(key + source + placeholder_signature + context_version)"
}

## Semantics
- Missing = targets[lang] is null or empty string (configurable).
- Only fill missing unless --force.
- If fingerprint changes (sv edited), mark related target statuses as "needs_review" (do not overwrite).
